<MainLayout title="Tails.com">
  <section class="bg-SalmonTreat-200 px-5 md:px-custom104 pt-4 md:pt-16 mb-16 md:mb-44" id="puppyhero">
    <div class="lg:grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="animationinviewfade">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-custom54 pb-8 md:pb-16 font-paytone uppercase">WHAT MAKES THE BEST PUPPY FOOD?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-xl pb-4 md:pb-8">Our food gives your puppy the nutrition they need to run and roll and grow and learn. Tell us about your pup and we'll create a recipe of dry food that develops with them as they grow.</p>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-xl pb-8 md:pb-16">You get clear portion recommendations and our adjustable scoop too, so it's easy to serve the right amount every day - for a healthy, happy puppy.</p>
        <div class="pb-4 md:pb-16 flex items-center md:items-start justify-center md:justify-start">
          <a href="/form">
            <Button variant="subprimary" size="large">Try It Now</Button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-end justify-center">
        <Image class="hidden lg:block w-full md:w-[500px] h-auto" src={puppy} alt="Puppy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-5 md:mx-custom104 mb-16 md:mb-44" id="eathealthy">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-custom54 font-paytone uppercase md:max-w-3xl pb-4 md:pb-16 animationinviewfade">YOU SHOULDN’T BE THE ONLY ONE EATING HEALTHY</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:grid grid-cols-4 md:gap-16">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1 animationinviewfade">
        <h3 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">Immune system</h3>
        <p class="pb-8 lg:pb-custom104 text-xs md:text-base lg:max-w-64">Beta-glucans and nucleotides help to enhance and regulate your puppy’s immune system - and offer extra protection by improving their response to vaccinations too.</p>
        <h3 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">Mental development</h3>
        <p class="pb-8 md:pb-0 text-xs md:text-base lg:max-w-64">Not many puppy foods include DHA omega-3. But ours does. This fatty acid is proven to aid learning and socialisation, and reduce the risk of behavioural problems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 col-span-2 flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="relative group pb-4 md:pb-0">
          <!-- Picture of food bowl -->
          <Image src={circlebowl} alt="First Image" class="w-[350px] md:w-[500px]" />
          <!-- Picture that goes on top of food bowl on hover  -->
          <Image src={circlecontent} alt="Second Image" class="absolute inset-0 object-cover opacity-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out group-hover:opacity-100 w-[350px] md:w-[500px]" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-3 animationinviewfade">
        <h3 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">Digestive system</h3>
        <p class="pb-8 lg:pb-custom104 text-xs md:text-base lg:max-w-64">We use chicken to aid your pup’s delicate digestion. And we also include prebiotics like FOS and MOS to help promote good bacteria - this is very important for your puppies.</p>
        <h3 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">Energy for growth</h3>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-base lg:max-w-64">Our energy-dense puppy kibble carefully balances calcium, vitamins, and minerals to help build strong bones and support your puppy’s rapid growth and development.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Quote2>14,000 HAPPY PUPPIES & <span class="text-SalmonTreat-500">1.7 MILLION</span> MEALS FED BY US EVERY MONTH</Quote2>

