        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-8 text-center md:text-left">
        <h3 class="stagger-item text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">6-14 Weeks Old</h3>
        <p class="stagger-item text-xs md:text-base pb-8 md:pb-16">A delivery every fortnight ensures your growing pup gets the nutrition they need, right when they need it.</p>
        <h3 class="stagger-item text-base md:text-2xl font-bold pb-3">14 Weeks Onwards</h3>
